Hi there. I'm Blocko, and I play osu!mania.
Feel free to contact me if you have any questions or concerns with a beatmap!
--------------------------------------
History
--------------------------------------
2014/02/26 - Joined osu!
2014/08/16 - Played as a 7K player on the USA Team for osu!mania World Cup 2014
2014/11/15 - Joined the osu!mania FEEL THE QUEUE Modding Team (closed)
2015/04/06 - Joined the Beatmap Nomination Group
2015/08/21 - Became one of the judges for Monthly Beatmapping Contest #11
2015/11/30 - Joined the Quality Assurance Team
2016/01/09 - Played as USA Team Captain for osu!mania 7K World Cup 2016
2016/12/13 - Took part as a Map Selector along with -Kamikaze- and Evening for osu!mania 7K World Cup 2017

--------------------------------------
Personal Achievements
--------------------------------------
2014/05/03 - Submitted my first map: Happy End of the World
2015/02/24 - First ranked guest difficulty: HHH - Ignited Night (7K EXpert)
2015/12/22 - After 19 months, Happy End of the World is finally qualified! (Ranked in 2015/12/31, my timezone)
2016/03/09 - Obtained my first 600pp play
2016/11/19 - Reached 10,000pp

--------------------------------------
Guest Difficulties
--------------------------------------
All charts are sorted from newest to oldest.
